When adding a '{{Sub-Task Blocking Condition}}' to a workflow transition, it doesnt display the issue status's icon as its passing to the #displayConstantIcon() macro a GenericValue not the Status object.

Offending files:
* {{subtaskblocking-condition-edit-params.vm}}
* {{subtaskblocking-condition-input-params.vm}}

Note: There may be additional files that does the same thing. Please find usages of the macro at time of fix.

